children.subject: This question has also been asked in @7311, so it sounds like multiple people are having this issue.  I also enrolled earlier today and the class didn't show up immediately, but it's since appeared.  You should check again to see if it's fixed itself.

history.content: I tried enrolling for CS186 for Phase II today and while it shows up in my Fall 2018 Course Schedule in the Shopping Cart and also part of my Current Schedule in Schedule Planner, it doesn't actually show up in the My Academics portal on Calcentral. Is anyone else having this issue? And does this still mean I'm enrolled/waitlisted in CS186 even though it doesn't show up on the My Academics portal?
history.subject: Enrolling in course doesn't show up on My Academics page?
